Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我要量下尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你還好吧 真晝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,尺子好涼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,量完了 我給你做溫熱的香蕉牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,學號2 石動雙葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,學號29 神樂光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,請幫我們量尺寸
